{"tid":918630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【烏俄衝突】烏克蘭明天進入戰時狀態 普京「嚴正關切」並籲德國介入","createTime":"2018-11-27T11:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T11:42:01.000Z","uid":75969,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2f501f0ca85be1caa484dd51c324f293e4a9221e","tid":918630,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T11:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181127/large/1543272596_807a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181127%2Flarge%2F1543272596_807a.jpg&h=3eb096ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">美國駐聯合國大使黑利，將俄烏海上衝突歸咎俄羅斯。(路透社)</span><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭海軍船艇遭俄羅斯扣留後，烏克蘭總統波羅申科周一簽署戒嚴令，並獲國會通過，周三起實施，為期30天，全國進入戰時狀態。俄羅斯總統普京對烏克蘭準備實施戒嚴表示「嚴正關切」，他與德國總理默克爾通電話時，希望德國會介入並阻止基輔採取「魯莽」行動。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯海軍周日在克里米亞沿海，登上並扣留3艘烏克蘭海軍船隻，指烏克蘭非法闖入俄羅斯的亞速海水域。各界擔心，這次海上衝突可能引爆軍事衝突。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普周一首度公開評論事件，沒有特別批評俄羅斯，只說美國反對「俄烏任何一方將暴力升級」。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普將在本周末阿根廷20國集團峯會期間與俄羅斯總統會面。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國安理會周一召開緊急會議。美國駐聯合國大使黑利（Nikki Haley）則將這宗衝突完全歸咎於俄羅斯，表示扣留船隻是「對烏克蘭領土主權的無恥侵犯」，並抨擊「俄羅斯再次魯莽升高（緊張）」。<br />\n<br />\n黑利表示：「對於和俄羅斯建立正常關係一事，美國深表歡迎，但類似這宗事件的不法行動，繼續讓此事（建立正常關係）不可能實現。」<br />\n<br />\n不過黑利並未威脅進一步制裁俄羅斯，只呼籲俄羅斯讓緊張降溫。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯2014年吞併克里米亞地區，但未獲國際承認。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/法新社  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181127/58962661\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181127%2F58962661&d=F1GnmvzqQ5QKbwFq1rmAD9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=79a3a546\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181127%2F58962661&h=93c23cb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181127/58962661</a>"},{"pid":"d8f61e818ac9e4b3f8657b5800a3e34039c3b3b5","tid":918630,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T11:22:30.000Z","msg":"支持普京吞晒附衣國家重建蘇聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d430f546af88626e2109a5b694340e60f6f0fa3","tid":918630,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d8f61e818ac9e4b3f8657b5800a3e34039c3b3b5","tid":918630,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T11:22:30.000Z","msg":"支持普京吞晒附衣國家重建蘇聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T11:22:47.000Z","msg":"附近"},{"pid":"b5bdd479b5c6efb93e65a3d9dd3fb63b38483836","tid":918630,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T11:24:32.000Z","msg":"米已成灶<br />\n你張樓契呢<br />\n屈sir"},{"pid":"be7f4d8ccd1e7f44972b89d3ca8674ac9fa0e2d0","tid":918630,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T11:24:36.000Z","msg":"收復蘇聯故土冇乜嘢唔啱,支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11fe119d3e900a17a8a3a9e688232f04c26d2e00","tid":918630,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8f61e818ac9e4b3f8657b5800a3e34039c3b3b5","tid":918630,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T11:22:30.000Z","msg":"支持普京吞晒附衣國家重建蘇聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T11:25:59.000Z","msg":"Hi 樓契男"},{"pid":"88791dbaf8644f7cbe1f302cd71ce2858082239a","tid":918630,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T11:27:52.000Z","msg":"普京淆左底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed631e3ccfefd37300b3750a7304110253d131a","tid":918630,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T11:28:32.000Z","msg":"